- I don't know.

01:25:47.625 --> 01:25:49.919
Yes, you do, Danny!
It's lunchtime!

01:25:50.002 --> 01:25:52.129
All right, I'll tell you what.

01:25:52.213 --> 01:25:55.050
What do you say we keep on working,
finish the other side, hmm?

01:25:55.134 --> 01:25:57.595
No, Danny. Why?

01:25:57.678 --> 01:26:00.890
Then we can blow off the rest of
the day and grab some pancakes.

01:26:00.973 --> 01:26:04.060
It won't take us long. Just throw
a little extra thinner into the mix.

01:26:04.143 --> 01:26:07.189
It'll go like butter.

01:26:54.952 --> 01:26:56.830
Danny, I am sorry.

01:26:56.914 --> 01:26:59.083
It's okay. Just leave it.
I'll mop it up.

01:26:59.124 --> 01:27:01.252
- I'll go get some more.
- You don't need to...

01:27:01.335 --> 01:27:03.963
- I will get some more.
- All right.

01:27:04.046 --> 01:27:06.132
- You know where? Ground floor?
- Okay.

01:27:06.215 --> 01:27:08.259
You know the closet?

01:27:12.473 --> 01:27:14.809
Set to go. Set to go.

01:27:30.619 --> 01:27:32.162
Fuck.

01:27:36.209 --> 01:27:39.212
Are you there?
I'm on my mark.

01:27:46.804 --> 01:27:49.141
- I'm on. Are you there?
- I'm here. We're running late.

01:27:49.224 --> 01:27:50.684
I know. I hit a snag.

01:27:52.686 --> 01:27:55.648
I'm already all set up, though.
Just give me one second.

01:28:01.864 --> 01:28:05.409
All right, I just gotta punch in
these codes. Just sit tight.

01:28:25.599 --> 01:28:26.893
I got it.

01:28:26.976 --> 01:28:29.354
Hang on one more beat.

01:28:39.699 --> 01:28:41.493
It's clear.
Get in there.

01:29:08.649 --> 01:29:12.570
I'm inside the first cage.
Repeat: I am inside the first cage.

01:29:20.329 --> 01:29:21.789
You're all clear.

01:30:35.375 --> 01:30:39.129
- I'm set. Kill it.
- All right, on my mark.

01:30:51.059 --> 01:30:52.227
Go.

01:30:56.607 --> 01:30:57.733
I'm here.

01:30:59.527 --> 01:31:01.447
There we go.

01:31:01.530 --> 01:31:03.908
Perfect. Tell me when
you're in second position.

01:33:45.052 --> 01:33:46.930
Fuck.

01:34:30.647 --> 01:34:33.316
- How ya doing down there?
- Almost there.

01:34:50.794 --> 01:34:52.798
Do you know where is Brian?

01:34:54.007 --> 01:34:55.759
No idea.

01:35:54.995 --> 01:35:55.787
I'm ready.

01:35:56.538 --> 01:35:59.833
I need a second here.
Hold on.

01:36:00.417 --> 01:36:02.878
I'm all set. Cut the cameras.
Repeat:

01:36:02.962 --> 01:36:05.214
I'm all set.
Cut the cameras.

01:36:08.552 --> 01:36:10.679
Gotta go. Got to go.

01:36:13.975 --> 01:36:16.060
What's up? What's up?

01:36:17.270 --> 01:36:20.065
I got company.
I got company.

01:36:22.026 --> 01:36:24.028
Hang on one second.

01:36:24.112 --> 01:36:25.863
Just sit tight.
I'll be right back.

01:36:57.983 --> 01:36:59.820
Okay.

01:37:16.714 --> 01:37:18.716
Jack, where are you?

01:37:23.179 --> 01:37:25.641
Jack, come in. Jack.

01:37:41.326 --> 01:37:43.829
Jack, are you there?

01:38:04.770 --> 01:38:06.772
I'm pulling out.
Repeat: I'm pulling out.

01:38:06.814 --> 01:38:08.774
- I'm back. I'm back.
- It's too late.

01:38:08.816 --> 01:38:11.110
- I'm pulling out.
- No, it's not. We're good.

01:38:11.193 --> 01:38:12.862
Get ready to go.

01:38:14.530 --> 01:38:15.991
On my mark.

01:38:20.204 --> 01:38:21.330
Go, go, go.

01:38:35.805 --> 01:38:37.766
What the hell's wrong
with these machines?

01:38:50.405 --> 01:38:53.409
Hey, stop banging on it.
Check the connection.

01:39:14.725 --> 01:39:18.062
- You see something?
- I don't know.

01:39:36.918 --> 01:39:39.337
Call them.
Call Ironclad.

01:39:40.088 --> 01:39:43.175
- And look like idiots?
- I don't care. Call them.

01:40:38.781 --> 01:40:41.493
Maybe it's some of the equipment
down in the basement.

01:40:43.829 --> 01:40:45.831
Okay. Thanks.

01:40:47.541 --> 01:40:50.170
Someone will be here
in a few minutes.

01:41:36.640 --> 01:41:38.725
Where are you, kid?

01:43:24.974 --> 01:43:27.977
Make a move, make a sound,
and you are dead.

01:43:28.060 --> 01:43:30.104
Do you understand me?

01:43:32.023 --> 01:43:33.608
Turn around.

01:43:38.156 --> 01:43:39.699
Be quiet.

01:43:54.132 --> 01:43:56.093
I wish you had not
come down here, man.

01:43:59.930 --> 01:44:04.061
Get over there. Turn around.
Come on. Let's go. Turn around.

01:44:04.144 --> 01:44:08.023
Walk over there.
Open the door.

01:44:08.107 --> 01:44:10.151
Open it.

01:44:10.192 --> 01:44:12.111
Get inside.

01:44:14.197 --> 01:44:16.116
Look at me.

01:44:16.200 --> 01:44:18.661
You're a good man.
I don't want to hurt you.

01:44:18.702 --> 01:44:21.622
But if you start making noise or
try to open that door, I will do it.

01:44:21.706 --> 01:44:23.207
Do you understand me?

01:44:25.585 --> 01:44:28.673
Stay in there and be quiet.
Everything will be fine.

01:45:32.079 --> 01:45:33.915
I don't wanna wait.

01:45:33.956 --> 01:45:36.751
I want you and Tommy
to go into the basement now.

01:45:36.793 --> 01:45:39.087
Come on, Andre.
I'm watching this.

01:45:39.170 --> 01:45:40.964
Laurent, please.

01:45:42.966 --> 01:45:46.262
Tommy, get Philippe. We're gonna be
checking out the basement again.

01:46:30.772 --> 01:46:32.607
Hold it right there!

01:46:32.690 --> 01:46:34.901
- Are you crazy?
- Take it off and put it down.

01:46:34.985 --> 01:46:38.948
- Aw, come on.
- Take it off and put it down now!

01:46:39.032 --> 01:46:42.410
- Don't do this.
- Take it off and put it down!

01:46:42.494 --> 01:46:44.454
- Please, don't...
- Don't fucking argue with me.

01:46:44.538 --> 01:46:47.207
Take it off and put it down.

01:46:47.290 --> 01:46:48.918
I can't. I can't.

01:46:50.211 --> 01:46:53.381
I'll put the next one in your knee.
I don't have time to fuck around.

01:46:53.465 --> 01:46:56.760
We can work out the details later.
I am leaving with that scepter.

01:46:58.053 --> 01:47:02.142
Now, take it off
and hand it over right now!

01:47:09.358 --> 01:47:12.945
Put it down. Slowly.

01:47:13.654 --> 01:47:15.949
Now, step back.
Back up.

01:47:24.876 --> 01:47:26.836
- Take off your mask.
- What?

01:47:26.920 --> 01:47:28.422
Take it off!

01:47:30.049 --> 01:47:33.386
I don't have time to play games.
Take it off.

01:47:45.734 --> 01:47:47.652
Throw it over there.

01:47:49.821 --> 01:47:51.990
Step in the middle.

01:47:52.074 --> 01:47:54.411
Step in the middle.
That's right.

01:47:58.081 --> 01:48:02.127
We wouldn't be here if you'd thrown
me some respect at the beginning.

01:48:02.211 --> 01:48:04.171
- Just a little bit.
- This is a stupid move.

01:48:04.255 --> 01:48:05.799
- It is? Why?
- We all come out ahead.

01:48:05.882 --> 01:48:08.343
What are you doing?
Just go up there and finish...

01:48:08.427 --> 01:48:10.028
It's a long shot.
I should play it tight.

01:48:10.053 --> 01:48:11.972
You know what I think
of your bullshit advice?

01:48:12.056 --> 01:48:15.184
I think that's you trying to talk me
into taking a sucker's share...

01:48:15.267 --> 01:48:18.522
on a score that I set up
from the beginning!

01:48:20.024 --> 01:48:24.070
You think I'm stupid, that I don't
see what you and Max are doing?

01:48:25.738 --> 01:48:29.409
I mean, what is he giving you?
Five, six million?

01:48:29.492 --> 01:48:31.912
Tell me that's not true.

01:48:31.996 --> 01:48:34.207
See, that doesn't work for me.

01:48:35.833 --> 01:48:40.672
I appreciate your help,
but you should've made me a partner.

01:48:40.755 --> 01:48:42.799
Now I gotta take a shot.

01:48:48.515 --> 01:48:52.018
Just sit tight. Just sit tight.
Everything will be fine.

01:48:56.023 --> 01:48:59.611
Now you got a choice. You can
either head for that tunnel...

01:48:59.694 --> 01:49:01.571
or smile for that camera.

01:49:10.165 --> 01:49:11.708
Andre, what's happening?

01:49:11.792 --> 01:49:13.419
Get down!
Go to the basement!

01:49:13.502 --> 01:49:16.088
We're being robbed!
We're being robbed!

01:49:21.093 --> 01:49:24.098
Henri, quick! Go outside!
Wait for the police!

01:49:31.648 --> 01:49:33.399
Let's go!
Go! Go! Go! Go!

01:50:04.811 --> 01:50:06.897
Over here! Over here!

01:50:11.068 --> 01:50:15.282
- He's in the tunnel!
- Where is he?

01:50:17.660 --> 01:50:19.119
Find him!

01:50:36.014 --> 01:50:38.141
- Back there!
- Okay!

01:50:38.224 --> 01:50:40.228
Come on! Come on! Come on!

01:51:24.236 --> 01:51:26.948
- Andre!
- Oh, shit.

01:51:27.031 --> 01:51:29.117
- Andre, is there a fire?
- It's okay.

01:51:33.039 --> 01:51:34.957
- Where's Danny?
- Just get out!

01:51:35.041 --> 01:51:37.418
- Okay.
- Just wait outside.

01:51:40.964 --> 01:51:44.427
- Just wait outside!
- Okay, bye-bye.

01:51:47.555 --> 01:51:49.891
Wait, Brian, wait!

01:51:49.933 --> 01:51:51.726
Get back, Brian!

01:51:54.271 --> 01:51:57.025
It's Brian! It's Brian!

01:51:57.108 --> 01:52:00.904
- Have you seen Brian?
- He's okay! He's outside!

01:52:00.987 --> 01:52:03.198
No! My God, it's him!

01:52:05.284 --> 01:52:08.037
It's okay now.
It's okay.

01:54:39.921 --> 01:54:43.759
Attention. The bus to Albany,
New York leaves in five...

01:54:45.762 --> 01:54:46.763
Yeah?

01:54:46.846 --> 01:54:49.099
- Hey, did you make it?
- Fuck you.

01:54:50.517 --> 01:54:52.477
Come on. I'm just checking
to make sure you got out okay.

01:54:52.519 --> 01:54:54.479
I knew you'd give 'em the slip.

01:54:55.689 --> 01:54:57.650
I'm almost home, too, here,
by the way.

01:54:57.734 --> 01:54:59.527
Oh, you are, huh?
You sure about that?

01:54:59.611 --> 01:55:03.073
Look, whatever you're thinking
about, just forget it, okay?

01:55:03.156 --> 01:55:05.159
This is over now
and you just gotta deal with it.

01:55:05.200 --> 01:55:08.747
It's not over yet 'cause you don't
know where you're going, and I do.

01:55:08.830 --> 01:55:10.749
- You don't know shit!
- You know where you're going?

01:55:10.832 --> 01:55:15.421
I'm five minutes from being gone.
You can't imagine where I'm going.

01:55:15.504 --> 01:55:18.257
- You got nothing.
- You know what I got.

01:55:18.340 --> 01:55:20.468
You just can't deal with the fact
that I beat you.

01:55:20.551 --> 01:55:24.640
Oh, yeah? What have you got?
Huh? What have you got?

01:55:24.723 --> 01:55:26.767
You know what I've got.

01:55:55.759 --> 01:55:57.010
Let me ask you something.

01:55:57.094 --> 01:56:00.515
When did you start thinking
you were better than me, huh?

01:56:00.598 --> 01:56:01.766
You still there, ace?

01:56:03.518 --> 01:56:06.521
Okay. Nicely done.

01:56:06.605 --> 01:56:09.233
Nicely done.
Now let's talk about this.

01:56:09.316 --> 01:56:11.756
Okay, let's see. How'd you put it?
" Deal with it. It's over."

01:56:11.777 --> 01:56:14.906
No, I don't think so. You want me
to list the ways I can burn you?

01:56:14.948 --> 01:56:18.118
We either work this out right now,
or I will take you down.

01:56:18.202 --> 01:56:21.622
Oh, yeah? How?
My shop, my tools, they're gone.

01:56:21.705 --> 01:56:24.458
Me, my friend, I'm just
a taxpaying jazz club owner.

01:56:24.542 --> 01:56:27.546
You? Every cop in the city's
looking for you right about now.

01:56:28.297 --> 01:56:31.592
So if I were you, I'd quit
making threats and hit the road.

01:56:35.555 --> 01:56:37.599
Nice working with you, ace.

01:56:37.640 --> 01:56:39.935
Okay, bye-bye.

01:57:12.848 --> 01:57:15.726
Montreal was stunned
by the daring predawn robbery...

01:57:15.768 --> 01:57:18.647
of the old city's historic
customshouse.

01:57:18.730 --> 01:57:22.276
A priceless scepter was stolen.
A senior night janitor...

01:57:22.359 --> 01:57:24.278
identified this man...

01:57:24.361 --> 01:57:26.280
as the prime suspect
in the burglary.

01:57:26.364 --> 01:57:29.575
He was spotted leaving the scene
moments after the robbery...

01:57:29.660 --> 01:57:32.121
and is now the focus
of a massive manhunt.

01:57:32.163 --> 01:57:35.917
A second suspect vanished
from the scene without a trace.

01:57:36.000 --> 01:57:39.170
Police have no solid leads.

